Package: HotellingEllipse
Title: Hotelling’s T2 Statistic and Confidence Ellipse
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Christian L.",
           family = "Goueguel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christian.goueguel@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0521-3446"))
Description: Computes Hotelling’s T-squared statistic jointly for PCA, ICA or, PLS components. It provides x-y coordinates or the value of the principal axes for drawing Hotelling's T-squared ellipse.
